---
import PageShell from '../layouts/PageShell.astro';
---

<PageShell
  title="Contacto | Logical Nutrition"
  description="Contáctanos por WhatsApp, email o redes sociales. Estamos para resolver tus dudas sobre suplementación."
  label="Contacto"
  canonical="/contacto"
>
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <div class="contact-intro animate-on-scroll">
      <p class="lead">¿Tienes dudas sobre dosis, combinaciones o envíos? Escríbenos directamente.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid">
      <a href="https://wa.me/56912345678?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20consultar%20por%20los%20suplementos%20de%20Logical%20Nutrition." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-card animate-on-scroll stagger-1">
        <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">💬</span>
        <h2>WhatsApp</h2>
        <p>Respuesta rápida para pedidos, dudas y asesoría personalizada.</p>
        <span class="contact-link">Escribir por WhatsApp</span>
      </a>

      <a href="mailto:hola@logicalnutrition.com" class="contact-card animate-on-scroll stagger-2">
        <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">✉️</span>
        <h2>Email</h2>
        <p>Para consultas más detalladas, partnerships o prensa.</p>
        <span class="contact-link">hola@logicalnutrition.com</span>
      </a>

      <div class="contact-card animate-on-scroll stagger-3">
        <span class="contact-icon" aria-hidden="true">📍</span>
        <h2>Ubicación</h2>
        <p>Envíos a todo el Perú desde nuestras bodegas en Lima.</p>
        <span class="contact-link">Perú</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <form class="contact-form animate-on-scroll" action="#" method="post" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
      <h2>Envíanos un mensaje</h2>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="name">Nombre</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="input" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="input" required />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label for="subject">Asunto</label>
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" class="input" required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label for="message">Mensaje</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" class="input" rows="5" required></textarea>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-accent">Enviar mensaje</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</PageShell>

<style>
  .container-narrow {
    max-width: var(--container-narrow);
  }

  .contact-intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .contact-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base), transform var(--transition-base) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-hover);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .contact-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    display: block;
  }

  .contact-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .contact-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .contact-form {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .contact-form h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .form-field label {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .form-field textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 120px;
  }
</style>
